Package: aeroinputs
Title: Prepare AERO Wind Erosion Model Inputs from LDC and SOLUS Data
Version: 1.1.0
Authors@R: 
    c(
        person("Geovany", "Ramirez", , "georam@nmsu.edu", role = c("aut", "cre")),
        person("Brandi", "Wheeler", , "bwheeler@nmsu.edu", role = "aut"),
        person("Sarah", "McCord", , "sarah.mccord@usda.gov", role = "aut")
    )
Description: Fetches LDC (Landscape Data Commons) plot-level datasets, retrieves
    SOLUS 100 soil-texture rasters, and assembles the gap, INI configuration,
    and summary CSV files required by the AERO wind-erosion model.
